	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here is a mod for adding FDS sounds to NES when using powerpak with ON and OFF switch. 47k resistor mounted under NES inside expansion connector bay.
<br />
<br />See video for step by step instructions.
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Z507PxcLjs">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Z507PxcLjs</a><!-- m -->

		

