	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm using v1.34 mappers. You should update to the current versions and see how that sounds for you. 
<br />
<br />I read on another forum, BunnyBoy suggested using a pot instead of a resistor so you can dial in the sound level. Personally, I don't want to add a pot to my NES, but it would be a good idea if you want to make sure the sound level is perfect. Also, you could adjust it if a future mapper version tweaks the level.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
